{"title":"关于我","date":"2021-04-29T13:45:20.000Z","updated":"2022-07-11T08:23:36.162Z","comments":true,"path":"api/pages/---.json","covers":null,"excerpt":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"个人信息\">个人信息</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>男</li>\r\n<li>00后</li>\r\n<li>本科 EE专业</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"爱好\">爱好</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Coding</li>\r\n<li>。。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"熟悉语言\">熟悉语言</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Python</li>\r\n<li>JavaScript</li>\r\n<li>C</li>\r\n<li>Java</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"开发中项目\">开发（中）项目</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><p><a\r\nhref=\"https://github.com/1390113493/beingain\">beingain云自习室后端部分</a>——\r\n基于“微型移动学习模式”的线上自习室的建设研究</p>\r\n<p>开发时间：2020-8</p>\r\n<p>使用语言：php</p>\r\n<p>使用框架：ThinkPHP</p>\r\n<p>登录部分代码：</p>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight php\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$loginname</span> = <span class=\"keyword\">$this</span>-&gt;request-&gt;param(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;loginname&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$password</span> = <span class=\"keyword\">$this</span>-&gt;request-&gt;param(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;password&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$ip</span> = <span class=\"keyword\">$this</span>-&gt;request-&gt;ip();</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$agent</span> = <span class=\"variable\">$_SERVER</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;HTTP_USER_AGENT&#x27;</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (!(<span class=\"variable\">$loginname</span> &amp;&amp; <span class=\"variable\">$password</span>) )&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> [</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">&#x27;code&#x27;</span>=&gt;-<span class=\"number\">1</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">&#x27;msg&#x27;</span>=&gt;<span class=\"string\">&#x27;用户名或密码不能为空！&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    ];</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\r\n<li><p>签到系统</p>\r\n<p>开发时间：2021-2</p>\r\n<p>使用语言：python</p>\r\n<p>使用框架：Django</p>\r\n<p>签到操作部分代码</p>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">checkin</span>(<span class=\"params\">time1, key, agent</span>):</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">    签到操作</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">    :param time1: 时间码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">    :param key: 密钥</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">    :param agent: 签到设备信息</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">    :return:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">    &quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># 对key进行解密，获得用户信息</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    decodeRes = decoding(time1, key)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"keyword\">not</span> decodeRes:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"string\">&#x27;code&#x27;</span>: -<span class=\"number\">1</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"string\">&#x27;msg&#x27;</span>: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;用户身份认证失败&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">try</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        user = Users.objects.get(<span class=\"built_in\">id</span>=<span class=\"built_in\">int</span>(decodeRes))</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">except</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"string\">&#x27;code&#x27;</span>: -<span class=\"number\">1</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"string\">&#x27;msg&#x27;</span>: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;查找用户失败&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># 获得签到记录</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> user.type_id == <span class=\"number\">1</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> check_by_times(<span class=\"number\">2</span>, user, agent)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">elif</span> user.type_id == <span class=\"number\">2</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\"># 这周还未签过</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> check_by_times(<span class=\"number\">4</span>, user, agent)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\r\n<li><p>学生权益后端部分</p>\r\n<p>开发时间：2020-10</p>\r\n<p>使用语言：python</p>\r\n<p>使用框架：Django</p>\r\n<p>获得话题部分代码</p>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">getList</span>(<span class=\"params\">page, token</span>):</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    userId = getUserId(token)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> userId[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;code&#x27;</span>] == <span class=\"number\">0</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        lists = Topic.objects.<span class=\"built_in\">filter</span>(check__in=[<span class=\"number\">1</span>, <span class=\"number\">3</span>], user_delete=<span class=\"literal\">None</span>, system_delete=<span class=\"literal\">None</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        count = lists.count()</span><br><span class=\"line\">        listdata = <span class=\"built_in\">list</span>(lists.values(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;id&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;pid&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;name&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;headimg&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;title&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;content&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;imgs&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;top&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;like&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;dislike&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;visit&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;create_time&#x27;</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\">        listdata.sort(key=<span class=\"keyword\">lambda</span> keys: keys[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;id&#x27;</span>], reverse=<span class=\"literal\">True</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        data = listdata[(page-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)*<span class=\"number\">10</span>:page*<span class=\"number\">10</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> data:</span><br><span class=\"line\">            i[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;desca&#x27;</span>] = i[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;content&#x27;</span>][:<span class=\"number\">30</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\">            i[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;categort&#x27;</span>] = Category.objects.get(<span class=\"built_in\">id</span>=i[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;pid&#x27;</span>]).name</span><br><span class=\"line\">            i[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;imgs&#x27;</span>] = <span class=\"built_in\">eval</span>(i[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;imgs&#x27;</span>]) <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> i[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;imgs&#x27;</span>] <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"literal\">None</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">del</span> i[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;content&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">del</span> i[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;pid&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"string\">&#x27;code&#x27;</span>: <span class=\"number\">0</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"string\">&#x27;msg&#x27;</span>: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;获取第&#x27;</span>+<span class=\"built_in\">str</span>(page)+<span class=\"string\">&#x27;页的数据成功&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"string\">&#x27;count&#x27;</span>: count,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"string\">&#x27;data&#x27;</span>: data</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> userId</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\r\n<li><p>One·School 一点到校——2021年计算机大赛参赛作品</p>\r\n<p>开发时间：2020-7-2021.5</p>\r\n<p>使用语言：python</p>\r\n<p>使用框架：Django</p></li>\r\n<li><p>EasyDo 易睹</p>\r\n<p>开发时间：2022-4-2022.7</p>\r\n<p>使用语言：python</p>\r\n<p>使用框架：Django</p></li>\r\n<li><p>其他</p></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n"}